videos.headline: Wilson finds Bowden for a 5-yard TD
videos.description: Terry Wilson throws an over-the-shoulder fade to Lynn Bowden Jr. for a 5-yard touchdown to tie the game at 7-7.

videos.headline: Shurmur extends play, finds Bolar for 49 yards
videos.description: Vanderbilt QB Kyle Shurmur scrambles and rips pass to C.J. Bolar for a 49-yard gain.

videos.headline: Kentucky's Bohanna blows up play and recovers fumble
videos.description: Vanderbilt's Jamauri Wakefield meets a wall of Kentucky defenders and fumbles as Quinton Bohanna recovers the ball.

videos.headline: Snell punches in a 7-yard TD
videos.description: Benny Snell Jr. takes the handoff and drives in a 7-yard touchdown to give Kentucky a 14-7 lead.

videos.headline: Shurmur fumble seals win for Kentucky
videos.description: With a 1:04 left in the 4th, Vanderbilt QB Kyle Shurmur is sacked by Josh Allen and fumbles and it is recovered by Kentucky to seal a 14-7 win.
